---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<Fragment slot="head">
		<title>Services | Alex Flooring & Carpentry LLC</title>
		<meta name="description" content="Full-service home remodeling: flooring, carpentry, painting, kitchens, bathrooms, and outdoor projects in Northern Virginia. Request an estimate." />
	</Fragment>

	<main id="main-content" class="bg-neutral">
		<section class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-10 sm:py-12 md:py-16">
			<nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="text-sm text-primary/80">
				<a href="/" class="hover:underline focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-accent">Home</a>
				<span aria-hidden="true" class="mx-2">/</span>
				<span aria-current="page" class="font-medium">Services</span>
			</nav>

			<h1 class="mt-4 text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-primary">Services</h1>
			<p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-base sm:text-lg text-primary/80">
				Explore our full-service remodeling solutions: flooring, carpentry, painting, kitchens, bathrooms, and outdoor projectsâ€”crafted to solve home challenges with durable, beautiful results.
			</p>

			<div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
				<article class="rounded-lg border border-primary/10 bg-neutral shadow-sm p-6 sm:p-8 transition-shadow transition-transform duration-200 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-0.5 focus-within:shadow-md focus-within:-translate-y-0.5">
					<h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-primary">Flooring Services</h2>
					<div class="mt-2 h-0.5 w-12 bg-accent"></div>
					<p class="mt-3 text-primary/80">
						<strong class="text-primary">Problem:</strong> Worn, uneven, or outdated floors diminish comfort and home value.
						<strong class="ml-2 text-primary">Solution:</strong> Professional installation, repair, and refinishing tailored to your space.
						<strong class="ml-2 text-primary">Benefits:</strong> Durable, stylish floors that are easy to maintain and built to last.
					</p>
					<div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
						<a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-primary bg-neutral px-5 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-primary hover:bg-primary hover:text-neutral hover:ring-1 hover:ring-accent focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-accent" aria-label="Request an estimate for flooring services">
							Request an Estimate
						</a>
						<a href="/portfolio" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-accent px-5 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-primary hover:bg-neutral hover:ring-1 hover:ring-accent focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-accent" aria-label="View our flooring portfolio">
							View Portfolio
						</a>
					</div>
				</article>

				<article class="rounded-lg border border-primary/10 bg-neutral/50 shadow-sm p-6 sm:p-8 transition-shadow transition-transform duration-200 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-0.5 focus-within:shadow-md focus-within:-translate-y-0.5">
					<h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-primary">Carpentry & Custom Woodwork</h2>
					<div class="mt-2 h-0.5 w-12 bg-accent"></div>
					<p class="mt-3 text-primary/80">
						<strong class="text-primary">Problem:</strong> Lack of storage, damaged trim, or unfinished spaces reduce functionality.
						<strong class="ml-2 text-primary">Solution:</strong> Custom trim, built-ins, stairs, framing, and repairs by skilled carpenters.
						<strong class="ml-2 text-primary">Benefits:</strong> Added utility, improved aesthetics, and increased home value with precise craftsmanship.
					</p>
					<div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
						<a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-primary bg-neutral px-5 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-primary hover:bg-primary hover:text-neutral hover:ring-1 hover:ring-accent focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-accent" aria-label="Request an estimate for carpentry services">
							Request an Estimate
						</a>
						<a href="/portfolio" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-accent px-5 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-primary hover:bg-neutral hover:ring-1 hover:ring-accent focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-accent" aria-label="View our carpentry portfolio">
							View Portfolio
						</a>
					</div>
				</article>

				<article class="rounded-lg border border-primary/10 bg-neutral shadow-sm p-6 sm:p-8 transition-shadow transition-transform duration-200 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-0.5 focus-within:shadow-md focus-within:-translate-y-0.5">
					<h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-primary">Painting & Finishing</h2>
					<div class="mt-2 h-0.5 w-12 bg-accent"></div>
					<p class="mt-3 text-primary/80">
						<strong class="text-primary">Problem:</strong> Faded paint and imperfect finishes make rooms feel tired and unwelcoming.
						<strong class="ml-2 text-primary">Solution:</strong> Interior/exterior painting, trim finishing, staining, and protective coatings.
						<strong class="ml-2 text-primary">Benefits:</strong> Fresh, durable finishes that brighten spaces and protect surfaces.
					</p>
					<div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
						<a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-primary bg-neutral px-5 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-primary hover:bg-primary hover:text-neutral hover:ring-1 hover:ring-accent focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-accent" aria-label="Request an estimate for painting services">
							Request an Estimate
						</a>
						<a href="/portfolio" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-accent px-5 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-primary hover:bg-neutral hover:ring-1 hover:ring-accent focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-accent" aria-label="View our painting portfolio">
							View Portfolio
						</a>
					</div>
				</article>

				<article class="rounded-lg border border-primary/10 bg-neutral/50 shadow-sm p-6 sm:p-8 transition-shadow transition-transform duration-200 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-0.5 focus-within:shadow-md focus-within:-translate-y-0.5">
					<h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-primary">Kitchen & Bathroom Remodeling</h2>
					<div class="mt-2 h-0.5 w-12 bg-accent"></div>
					<p class="mt-3 text-primary/80">
						<strong class="text-primary">Problem:</strong> Outdated layouts, limited storage, and worn fixtures limit comfort and efficiency.
						<strong class="ml-2 text-primary">Solution:</strong> Smart planning, cabinetry, surfaces, lighting, and fixtures for modern, functional spaces.
						<strong class="ml-2 text-primary">Benefits:</strong> Elevated style, improved workflow, and increased home value.
					</p>
					<div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
						<a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-primary bg-neutral px-5 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-primary hover:bg-primary hover:text-neutral hover:ring-1 hover:ring-accent focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-accent" aria-label="Request an estimate for kitchen and bathroom remodeling">
							Request an Estimate
						</a>
						<a href="/portfolio" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-accent px-5 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-primary hover:bg-neutral hover:ring-1 hover:ring-accent focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-accent" aria-label="View our remodeling portfolio">
							View Portfolio
						</a>
					</div>
				</article>

				<article class="rounded-lg border border-primary/10 bg-neutral shadow-sm p-6 sm:p-8 transition-shadow transition-transform duration-200 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-0.5 focus-within:shadow-md focus-within:-translate-y-0.5">
					<h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-primary">Decks & Outdoor Projects</h2>
					<div class="mt-2 h-0.5 w-12 bg-accent"></div>
					<p class="mt-3 text-primary/80">
						<strong class="text-primary">Problem:</strong> Aging decks and unused outdoor areas limit entertaining and relaxation.
						<strong class="ml-2 text-primary">Solution:</strong> New deck builds, repairs, railings, and exterior carpentry to maximize outdoor spaces.
						<strong class="ml-2 text-primary">Benefits:</strong> Safe, durable, and beautiful outdoor living areas tailored to your lifestyle.
					</p>
					<div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
						<a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-primary bg-neutral px-5 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-primary hover:bg-primary hover:text-neutral hover:ring-1 hover:ring-accent focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-accent" aria-label="Request an estimate for decks and outdoor projects">
							Request an Estimate
						</a>
						<a href="/portfolio" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-accent px-5 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-primary hover:bg-neutral hover:ring-1 hover:ring-accent focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-accent" aria-label="View our outdoor projects portfolio">
							View Portfolio
						</a>
					</div>
				</article>
			</div>

			<section aria-labelledby="faq-heading" class="mt-14">
				<h2 id="faq-heading" class="sr-only">Additional Information</h2>
				<p class="text-sm text-primary/70">
					Looking for details on specific sub-services? We can add <span class="font-semibold">h3</span> sections for items like Hardwood Installation, Tile, Baseboards, Crown Molding, and more.
				</p>
			</section>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>


